@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam TitleFontColor #000000

title Root Import Before Browser Split

actor "Next.js Client Bundle" as Client
component "@xylex-group/athena\n(dist/index.js)" as Root #FCE8E6
component "schema/index.ts\nre-export" as Schema #FDEBD0
component "generator/index.ts\nre-export" as Generator #FDEBD0
component "schema/postgres-provider.ts\nimport pg" as PgProvider #F8D7DA
component "generator/config.ts\nimport fs/path/url" as GenConfig #F8D7DA
component "generator/pipeline.ts\nimport fs/promises" as GenPipeline #F8D7DA
component "Next.js browser compiler" as Compiler #FFF3CD

Client --> Root : import { createClient }
Root --> Schema : static re-export
Root --> Generator : static re-export
Schema --> PgProvider : loads at module link time
Generator --> GenConfig : loads at module link time
Generator --> GenPipeline : loads at module link time
Compiler --> PgProvider : resolve pg/net/tls
Compiler --> GenConfig : resolve fs/path/url
Compiler --> GenPipeline : resolve fs/promises
Compiler --> Client : module-not-found errors

note bottom of Root
Even when only createClient is used,
the root barrel links Node-only modules.
end note
@enduml
